description: Retrieve all of the origination identities that are associated with a registration.

parameters.name: RegistrationId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the registration.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: An array of RegistrationAssociationFilter to apply to the results that are returned. (dict) --- The filter definition for filtering registrations that meets a specified criteria. The name of the attribute to filter on. An array of values to filter for. (string) ---

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the attribute to filter on.

nested_params.name: Values
nested_params.description: An array of values to filter for.

nested_items.name: RegistrationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the registration.

nested_items.name: RegistrationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the registration.

nested_items.name: RegistrationType
nested_items.description: The type of registration form. The list of RegistrationTypes can be found using the  DescribeRegistrationTypeDefinitions action.

nested_items.name: ResourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the origination identity that is associated with the registration.

nested_items.name: ResourceId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the origination identity. For example this could be a PhoneNumberId or SenderId.

nested_items.name: IsoCountryCode
nested_items.description: The two-character code, in ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 format, for the country or region.

nested_items.name: PhoneNumber
nested_items.description: The phone number associated with the registration in E.164 format.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to be used for the next set of paginated results. You don't need to supply a value for this field in the initial request.
